The paper deals with image segmentation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of co-sparse analysis and convex optimization suggests that the paper may also fall under machine learning (cs.MM) and machine learning theory (cs.LG). The Bayesian approach mentioned in the abstract also suggests that the paper may fall under artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the mention of parallelization on graphics hardware suggests that the paper may also fall under information theory (cs.IT).
